      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just everything. the way i talk, the way i work, the way i smile at people... it's all just code i've learned to run. like i'm just a program simulating a human. and the worst part is that if i stopped doing all that, there's nothing to catch me. there's just nothing. just an empty space where a person should be.",
